    {
      "type": "text", "id": "open_title", "x": 320, "y": 2256, "width": 860, "height": 26,
      "text": "DO I MISS ANYTHING? — open items & gaps",
      "originalText": "DO I MISS ANYTHING? — open items & gaps",
      "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#b91c1c", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 400023, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 400024, "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "open_items", "x": 320, "y": 2298, "width": 1540, "height": 230,
      "text": "❓  Is main DEPLOYED to prod?  oracle = `vercel ls` + live discriminator on command.nisria.co — NEVER the git push alone (KT #393)\n\n🟡  WhatsApp → MCP tools NOT connected yet (Slice C unbuilt). The bot cannot call the command.nisria.co tool layer; only Nur's claude.ai can.\n\n🟡  Intent classifier still observe-only — now redundant with the router. Decide: cut it, or promote it as a cheap pre-check.\n\n🟡  3 bug fixes stranded on stale branch fix/phone-canonical-dedup — rescue KT #206550 (send-truth) + KT #364 (Zoom time) before abandoning.\n\n🔒  Tier subset by design: team sees ~13 safe tools, admin (Nur) gets the full lane. Not a gap.",
      "originalText": "❓  Is main DEPLOYED to prod?  oracle = `vercel ls` + live discriminator on command.nisria.co — NEVER the git push alone (KT #393)\n\n🟡  WhatsApp → MCP tools NOT connected yet (Slice C unbuilt). The bot cannot call the command.nisria.co tool layer; only Nur's claude.ai can.\n\n🟡  Intent classifier still observe-only — now redundant with the router. Decide: cut it, or promote it as a cheap pre-check.\n\n🟡  3 bug fixes stranded on stale branch fix/phone-canonical-dedup — rescue KT #206550 (send-truth) + KT #364 (Zoom time) before abandoning.\n\n🔒  Tier subset by design: team sees ~13 safe tools, admin (Nur) gets the full lane. Not a gap.",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#0f172a", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 400025, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 400026, "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.4
    },

    {
