    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "tools_body", "x": 1310, "y": 352, "width": 560, "height": 130,
      "text": "115 SMART_TOOLS   (≈55 read · ≈60 action)\n  → role subset:  team ~13 safe · admin full\n  → mesh scope:  each lane loads only ~10-15  ← the narrowing",
      "originalText": "115 SMART_TOOLS   (≈55 read · ≈60 action)\n  → role subset:  team ~13 safe · admin full\n  → mesh scope:  each lane loads only ~10-15  ← the narrowing",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#475569", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 500005, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 500006, "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.45
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "guards_sub", "x": 1310, "y": 470, "width": 560, "height": 22,
      "text": "Honesty guards (always on):", "originalText": "Honesty guards (always on):",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#0f172a", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 500007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 500008, "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "guards_body", "x": 1310, "y": 500, "width": 560, "height": 160,
      "text": "•  send-state truth — claim \"sent\" only if the send\n    tool returned ok THIS turn (real lookup required)\n•  completion guard — a read can't excuse a self-mark lie\n•  no-scope-leak — a specialist can't act outside its lane\n•  task-explosion dedup + atomic dedupe\n•  test-mode — sandbox origin, no live send on a test msg",
      "originalText": "•  send-state truth — claim \"sent\" only if the send\n    tool returned ok THIS turn (real lookup required)\n•  completion guard — a read can't excuse a self-mark lie\n•  no-scope-leak — a specialist can't act outside its lane\n•  task-explosion dedup + atomic dedupe\n•  test-mode — sandbox origin, no live send on a test msg",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#475569", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 500009, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 500010, "isDeleted": false,
