      "text": "tables:  tasks · donations · beneficiaries · payments ·\nmessages · events · documents · contacts · campaigns ·\ninventory · pending_intents · agent_memory\n\n•  Brain (FTS) grounding injected into the prompt\n    (prompt-cached at the split marker)\n•  events = the telemetry / audit ledger (emit)\n•  RLS on · PII never reaches anon · KES/USD never mix",
      "originalText": "tables:  tasks · donations · beneficiaries · payments ·\nmessages · events · documents · contacts · campaigns ·\ninventory · pending_intents · agent_memory\n\n•  Brain (FTS) grounding injected into the prompt\n    (prompt-cached at the split marker)\n•  events = the telemetry / audit ledger (emit)\n•  RLS on · PII never reaches anon · KES/USD never mix",
